{"tid":1481971,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"字母化中文果班人，你同正苦有乜撚分別？","createTime":"2019-08-18T02:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T10:09:22.000Z","uid":292798,"like":6,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1ed75cd4cb05980bffb845e838cf3b7006a34b55","tid":1481971,"uid":292798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:36:33.000Z","msg":"共匪正苦去CUT聆聽說話卷，你班仆街幫手CUT埋文字將佢字母化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我屌你地係咪好撚好玩呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人就會識睇？你果啲係中英夾雜火星5P文咋﹗係撚正宗粵拼呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你試下攞你地啲火星文畀中文老師睇睇佢要解幾耐？<br />\n仲笑住話係加密令班中国佬睇唔明，仆街啦香港人都睇唔明呀﹗<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要消滅一個民族，首先瓦解它的文化；要瓦解它的文化，首先先消滅承載它的語言；要消滅這種語言，首先先從他們的學校裡下手。</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>共匪喺學校入手，你班仆街喺日常生活入手？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地自己傾計用火星文你嘅事，而家做緊正經大事呀﹗<br />\n上報紙上頭條呀﹗歷史記錄嚟嫁﹗<br />\n香港人睇唔明，外國人睇唔明，你叫人點關注你呀﹗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家你係咪覺得有老美撐住就心雄呀？學撚足雨革後期玩嘉年華呀？<br />\n你地係咪想香港變新疆呀？﹗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd3a6ab1d1413e2ba8b075f28763f61b7170d85","tid":1481971,"uid":292798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:45:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=2213554218935109&amp;id=100008416562588\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2213554218935109%26id%3D100008416562588&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1MF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=2537570c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=2213554218935109&amp;id=100008416562588</a><br />\n<br />\n鍾偉民都屌你地老母呀﹗唔識邊個鍾偉民自己查書啦﹗"},{"pid":"17ecef0538621b6bb85b90fa00edd09b6e747903","tid":1481971,"uid":292798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:46:56.000Z","msg":"負評果班垃圾你識唔識撚文化？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你係咪想毀滅香港嘅傳統文化呀？﹗</span></span>"},{"pid":"636e8641ef19d971d642af6a2e5d7c409c4d6ac1","tid":1481971,"uid":292798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:17:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人地外國人專登去學正體中文<br />\n紋身都紋正體字<br />\n你班仆街走去玩字母化玩膠？</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fce3e90f558e4014abc22ebfba5a0cbb6b73886c","tid":1481971,"uid":292798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:44:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>國家大事唔係用官方語言嚟做文宣，走去玩你地自己先睇得明嘅嘢<br />\n你地依家係咪切割同分化唔識睇果班抗爭者呀？﹗</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a801d7af3d7c837d0fb42f02cf0f9a61eb183a44","tid":1481971,"uid":89392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:45:16.000Z","msg":"係連登玩其實無傷大雅，最仆街係《蘋果》不分輕重用嚟出頭條啫"},{"pid":"75e0b3c15650c55510c048af9e08941154397d3f","tid":1481971,"uid":288688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T00:53:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f75fa2e7d493b9bd51a8212cef7c04d87739c91a","tid":1481